content:
LOST TOURIST IN HARLEM GETS TEETH KNOCKED OUT; RAPED:  She got lost looking for her Airbnb in Harlem, and that's when a 41-year old tourist from Germany ran into a robber who not only wanted her money, but then proceeded to beat her senseless and rape her on the sidewalk.  PIX 11 has a picture of suspect, Keon Robinson, a registered sex offender who's now a suspect in 3 robberies in the 32nd Precinct. 
If you know where he is, call 1-800-577-TIPS.  Magee Hickey reports for PIX11.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

content:
SECOND BODY IN TWO DAYS; Central Park Lakes:  What's the deal?  For the second time in two days, 
the NYPD has pulled a man's body out of a lake in Central Park.  The latest was Wednesday morning, when a man's body was discovered in Swan Lake by 59th Street and Fifth Avenue.  On Tuesday, a man's body was found floating in the #CentralPark reservoir near West 90th Street and Central Park West.  NYPD Chief of Detectives Robert Boyce was going to speak about the 2 incidents on Wednesday.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

content:
THEY GOT HIM!  A Fugitive Task Force caught the registered sex offender, #KeonRobinson, wanted for the 
robbery and sexual assault of a tourist from Germany.  They found him in Schenectady County, in upstate New York.  The NYPD said Robinson robbed three people during a brutal crime spree, ending with the 31-year old tourist on May 4th.  She had left the subway near West 149th Street at 2:50 am and was heading back to her Airbnb in Harlem, when she was assaulted.  The attack was so brutal that she had some of her teeth knocked out.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

content: 'I'LL SEE HIM IN HELL:'  The angry mother of #RashawnBrazell, whose body parts were left in a subway tunnel in 2005, left court infuriated, after the suspected serial killer accused of dismembering her son demanded a new lawyer.  Desire Brazell was there with the sisters of the late #SharabiaThomas, a beautiful 17 year old who disappeared in 2004 on her way to high school. Thomas was found strangled in a laundry bag.  Both victims lived in Bushwick, Brooklyn on Gates Avenue....the same avenue where the suspect, Kwauhuru Govan, once resided.  He's also tied to two, other cases, where the victims were dismembered.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

HORSES RUN WILD IN MIDTOWN: Two horses were bolting along midtown Manhattan streets Monday morning, dodging honking cars and buses, and one of them apparently collapsed into the side of a #taxi.  
John Collins of NYCLASS provided this video.  He said the incident provides another reason why carriage horses should not be working amid NYC traffic.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

content: LEAR JET CRASHES ON APPROACH TO #TETERBORO AIRPORT: At least 2 people are dead, after a Lear Jet crashed about a 1/4 mile from Teterboro, NJ runway.  A huge fireball was evident, inside an industrial area near the airport.  We're waiting to hear if anyone on the ground was hit by debris.  One aviation expert told PIX 11 there were reports the plane flipped over before it crashed, perhaps affected by a "microburst" weather event.  The plane had taken off for Philadelphia bound for Teterboro.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

content: RETIRED NYPD COPS UPSET ABOUT OVERTURNED CONVICTIONS: Three, retired NYPD detectives insist they didn't force two, 16 year old kids from #Brooklyn to confess to a carjacking and execution-style murder in 1985.  One of the kids spent 29 years in prison--and the other died in prison--before the DA asked a judge to vacate the convictions in 2014.  Millions of dollars have been given out to settle 22 cases that have been "vacated" in Brooklyn. Please check out my special PIX 11 report and tell me what you think about the McCallum/Stuckey case that was overturned and sealed.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

content: 23 PEOPLE HIT IN Times Square, New York City: An 18 year old girl is dead; her 13 year old sister among 22 hurt.  4 injuries are critical.  26 year old Richard Rojas of the Bronx, a US Navy vet, was speeding south on 7th Avenue and then made a U-turn, speeding north on the sidewalk and plowing into the pedestrians.  He has 2, previous DWI arrests.  Police are investigating whether he was making a getaway from a robbery.

A vendor describes the scene, as a wrong-way driver plowed north on the 7th Avenue sidewalk, ramming pedestrians, before a "terror barrier" stopped him, causing his car to flip over and burst into flames. PIX 11 has reporters all over the scene.

He killed an 18 year old tourist from Michigan.

content:
MOWED DOWN IN TIMES SQUARE:
18 year old Alyssa Elsman of Michigan was killed by a speeding car, going the wrong way, that also hit her 13 year old sister and 21 other pedestrians in Times Square, New York City on Thursday. Elsman was visiting the Big Apple with her family. 
The driver of the speeding Honda was high on the synthetic drug known as K2.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery
title: Timeline Photos

content: HIGH ON K2:  Police say 26 year old Richard Rojas, a U.S. Navy vet, was high on K2 when he rammed his car into 23 people in Times Square, New York City,  An 18 year old tourist from Michigan, Alyssa Ehlsman, was killed. Her 13 year old sister is among the 22 who were injured.

title: Timeline Photos

content: "I HAVE A SICKNESS"  A mob scene at federal court, after former U.S. Congressman and mayoral candidate, #AnthonyWeiner, pleaded guilty to 'sexting' with a girl he knew was 15.  Weiner sobbed as he read his statement to Judge Loretta Preska, telling her, "Beginning with my service in Congress and continuing into the first half of last year, I have compulsively sought attention from women who contacted me on social media."  Prosecutors have recommended Weiner be sentenced to between 21 and 27 months in prison.  A judge could give him no jail time...or up to 10 years.  Weiner's estranged wife--Hillary Clinton's chief aide, Huma Abedin--filed for divorce within hours of the guilty plea.  The couple has a young son.  Weiner said he is getting daily treatment for his "sickness." Thank you to PIX 11's Dan Mannarino for the footage.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

content:
TIMES SQUARE DRIVER FACING MURDER CHARGE--AND 20 COUNTS OF ATTEMPTED MURDER:
26 year old RIchard Rojas of the Bronx was in court Friday, accused of Murder in the 2nd degree and 20 counts of attempted murder, for mowing down pedestrians in Times Square, New York City Thursday at noontime.  18 year old Alyssa Ehlson of Michigan, in NYC with her mother and sister, died at the scene. Police said Rojas, a US Navy vet, was screaming and rambling about hearing voices, when he was grabbed on 7th Avenue.  He also told police he had "smoked something"--and toxicology tests will determine if that "something" was K2, a  synthetic drug that's made with chemicals sprayed on dried leaves..
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

At least 22 are dead and dozens more injured or maimed by nuts and bolts that were in the device.

MOM & DAD KILLED, WAITING FOR KIDS:
Marcin and Angelika Klis had arrived at #ManchesterArena Monday night to pick up their daughters from the Ariana Grande show, when a suicide bomber detonated his explosive. They didn't survive. Their daughter, Alex, was in a hospital in the early days, pleading for information about her parents. They are not the only parents who were killed, waiting for their children. Several other moms perished, as well.

JUMPING TURNSTILES IN DISGUISE: 
These 3 men, dressed as construction workers, are wanted for an $800,000 #jewelry heist at 60 Court Street in #Brooklyn. They're suspected of beating up a 67 year old jeweler before making off with the gems. They got away through the Borough Hall subway station, according to police. Another guy dressed as a construction worker stayed outside the store and was said to be the look-out.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery

content: FDNY 'WARRIOR' LOSES CANCER BATTLE:  Retired New York City Fire Department (FDNY) firefighter #RayPfeifer put a face on the 9/11 first responders' fight to get proper medical care, after hundreds became sick with cancer and other serious illnesses. He successfully lobbied Çongress, with the help of Jon Stewart and John Feal, to pass the Zadroga Act. I only meet Ray Pfeifer a little over a month ago, as he waged a final battle for his FDNY brothers. Rest in peace, Firefighter Pfeifer, gone at the age of 59.
name: Mary Murphy Mystery
title: Dying firefighter, sick from 9/11 illness, fights last battle: A spot on FDNY Wall of Honor

The first victim--22 years old--handed over the maximum withdrawal allowed, $1,000. In the second case, Monday May 29th, the 36 year old victim gave the guy $500.  The address is 1266 First Avenue, Manhattan.
